description: New Orleans City Council Districts - Effective May 5, 2014  Voters will be placed in the districts displayed by January 1, 2014 for all future elections.  Council districts are based upon the 2010 census and redistricting.  Precincts are drawn according to the New Orleans Home Rule Charter.
